## 04 — Engineering (Integration) (Draft)

### Contract rules
- API responses must follow standard `{ code, message, data }` format (see `src/lib/api/response`).
- Frontend must use `src/services/apiClient.ts` exclusively.

### Key integration flows to validate end-to-end
- Subscribe (wallet debit) → access to subscriber posts → subscription list shows active
- PPV purchase → access to media → PPV purchase history reflects it
- Tip → transaction created → creator earnings reflect it
- Bundle purchase → access to bundle posts → purchase history reflects it
- Live stream:
  - creator creates stream → goes live → fans can watch (gated) → notifications fire
- Push notifications:
  - permission + subscribe endpoint → notify on new post, live started, etc.

